cli.help.page.add_extension:
Xiknana tlamantli ipan pack extensions (provider extension path ye huehca/legacy/schema-core)

Tequitl: greentic-pack add-extension [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Tlanahuatilmeh:
  provider    Xiknana noso xikyancuic entrada tlen provider extension
  capability  Xiknana noso xikyancuic entrada tlen capability offer

Tlamachiyotlmeh:
  --locale <LOCALE>  Locale para mensajes CLI
cli.help.page.add_extension_capability:
Xiknana noso xikyancuic entrada tlen capability offer

Tequitl: greentic-pack add-extension capability [OPTIONS] --pack-dir <DIR> --offer-id <ID> --cap-id <CAP_ID> --component-ref <COMPONENT> --op <OP>

Xikitta `greentic-pack add-extension capability --help` para nochi detalles tlen argumentos.
